    "Finally, we see showers with large weights cluster at low sparsities.",
    "Here the generator has a systematic bias towards simpler showers with fewer voxels.",
    "The full set of studied observables for e +, γ, and π+ can be found in Appendix B.",
    "Given these observations, the leading improvement to the generative model concerns the low-energetic voxels.",
